  ('optometrist-moex-00523', 'optometrist', 'optometrist-moex-112-aa93ddf5', 'sub-optometrist-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '有一先天中樞性視覺障礙（cerebralvisualimpairment）的低視力幼兒，為其檢查瞳孔的光反射，最有可能 的結果是：', '["異常的瞳孔反應（paradoxicalpupillaryresponse）", "雙側遲鈍的瞳孔反應（bilateralsluggishreactivepupils）", "單側相對性瞳孔傳入障礙（unilateralrelativeafferentpupillarydefect）", "正常的瞳孔反應（normalpupillaryresponse）"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:17:42+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9dcd88633073", "answer_pdf_sha1": "482613c66a88", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "112110", "c": "109", "s": "0905", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "本試題為單一選擇題", "subject": "低視力學", "year": "112", "exam_name": "112年第二次專技人員高等考試營養師、護理師、社會工作師考試、112年專技人員高等考試法醫師、語言治療師、聽力師、牙體技術師、公共衛生師考試...", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "optometrist", "db_exam_id": "optometrist"}'::jsonb, NULL)
